\"The selection process for the team was extremely competitive, perhaps the toughest in the world.\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1097, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This has been great for the team.\\\"\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The two-time all-around world champion warned that Japan and China should be wary with the United States, Britain and Ukraine all in the running for the podium.\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1295, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1186, \"end\": 1191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9999999940803264, \"rank\": 5.91911532366798e-09, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 1196, \"end\": 1201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9954101110013359, \"rank\": 0.004268075044177227, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1226, \"end\": 1239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998929495235, \"rank\": 5.517527834013187e-08, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1241, \"end\": 1248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.999709661896355, \"rank\": 0.0002904066444427262, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9533085383862466, \"rank\": 0.0489724642205106, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not only Japanese and Chinese athletes who are competing.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1312, \"end\": 1320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9999999778501663, \"rank\": 2.211249468411248e-08, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 1325, \"end\": 1332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9993441034808269, \"rank\": 0.00036703290246625585, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other countries are here too,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1400, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hashimoto aims to match countryman Kohei Uchimura by retaining all-around gold, and keep it in Japanese hands for an unprecedented fourth consecutive Games.\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1437, \"end\": 1451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K\\u014dhei_Uchimura\", \"score\": 0.9999999961760295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kohei Uchimura\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K\\u014dhei_Uchimura\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K\\u014dhei_Uchimura\"}, {\"begin\": 1497, \"end\": 1505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9999999778501663, \"rank\": 2.211249468411248e-08, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zhang Boheng beat Hashimoto to the world title in 2021, and will spearhead the Chinese challenge along with 2017 world champion Xiao Ruoteng.\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1701, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1560, \"end\": 1572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Boheng\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zhang Boheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Boheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Boheng\"}, {\"begin\": 1639, \"end\": 1646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9993441034808269, \"rank\": 0.00036703290246625585, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1688, \"end\": 1700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xiao_Ruoteng\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Xiao Ruoteng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xiao_Ruoteng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xiao_Ruoteng\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Chinese team also includes world and Olympic rings gold medallist Liu Yang and Olympic parallel bars champion Zou Jingyuan.\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1706, \"end\": 1713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9993441034808269, \"rank\": 0.00036703290246625585, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1772, \"end\": 1780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emperor_Ming_of_Han\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1748360079805155e-18, \"text\": \"Liu Yang\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emperor_Ming_of_Han\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emperor_Ming_of_Han\"}, {\"begin\": 1816, \"end\": 1828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zou_Jingyuan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zou Jingyuan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zou_Jingyuan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zou_Jingyuan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All of us in Team China are prioritising the team event,\\\" said Xiao.\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1899, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I suffered a severe shoulder injury before coming to Paris, so I need to reserve more strength for the team competition.\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 2022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1955, \"end\": 1960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999724878, \"rank\": 2.748478091996919e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have prepared as a team with many outstanding members, including two Olympic champions and three world champions.\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The strengths and weaknesses are fairly balanced.\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2191, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Japanese team is younger and may have better stamina, but we have more experience.\\\"\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2196, \"end\": 2204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9999999778501663, \"rank\": 2.211249468411248e-08, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The United States have not won an Olympic men's team gymnastics medal since pocketing bronze in 2008, and finished fifth in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2285, \"end\": 2298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998929495235, \"rank\": 5.517527834013187e-08, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2405, \"end\": 2410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4487754579990127e-19, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Fifth place (left) a pretty bad taste in our mouth,\\\" said Brody Malone, returning from injury for the US in a team that includes last year's world all-around bronze medallist Frederick Richard.\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2472, \"end\": 2477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brody\", \"score\": 0.9918419058577215, \"rank\": 0.008215641350258051, \"text\": \"Brody\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brody\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brody\"}, {\"begin\": 2478, \"end\": 2484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"score\": 0.9953672421203632, \"rank\": 0.002601622940432406, \"text\": \"Malone\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\"}, {\"begin\": 2516, \"end\": 2518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999923188625, \"rank\": 7.672623260900044e-09, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2589, \"end\": 2598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4251650688759026e-17, \"text\": \"Frederick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", 